ulations using a variety of\nstrategies to analyze the SNO and other solar neutrino data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Apr 2002 19:55:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 May 2002 16:38:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 Jul 2002 14:44:08 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 26 Jul 2002 18:47:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
