 dip with existing data, we make the robust prediction for the spectrum at\n$1\\times 10^{18} - 1\\times 10^{20}$ eV to be measured in the nearest future by\nAuger detector.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Apr 2002 15:44:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Jan 2007 20:16:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 1 Feb 2007 12:30:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-17"}
